    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Explore the Dungeon alone or with your friends in DUNGEON ONLINE.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Create your character and dive into the Dungeon, fight various enemies like skeletons and goblins, fight dangerous Bosses,  and take your rewards to become even stronger.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Defeating enemies you obtain items and experience points to equip your character to increase your stats and conquer the Dungeon. </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Enemies can drop items like their weapons, healing herbs, materials and summoning item.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >You can even dissamble your weapons to obtain materials to upgrade your favourite weapons.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >You can invite your friends to your lobby by in-game menu (they must be playing &quot;Dungeon Online&quot;).</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >In a multiplayer session, only the Host can summon units or interact with objects like doors, checkpoints or lootable chest.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >There is Arena Mode also, to fight other players in 3 types of PvP: Duel, Trio or Brawl.</p>",
